window.bookSummaryJSON = "Not only is Charles Stross' <i>Iron Sunrise</i> a \"hard-science fiction masterpiece\" ( <i>Library Journal</i>), it's also \"a Hollywood thriller with a cyberpunk heart\" ( <i>Entertainment Weekly</i>). <p> Planet Moscow is vaporized by an unnatural star explosion, prompting those who escaped to counterattack the likely culprit - planet New Dresden of the neighboring system. But New Dresden wasn't to blame, and as worlds go to war, an unseen enemy labors to destroy the universe itself.</p>"; 
